Next Thursday (10/12),  NY is hosting the opening of ‘Apophenies’ by Cory Haber!

Cory’s custom built plotter will be on display as well as the first completed painting of the collection. First 15 attendees will receive a signed poster 😊

https://partiful.com/e/5E7Csq43TuuOsf4oxQg3

100 generative oil paintings will take Cory up to a year to complete. The ranked auction for ‘Apopehnies’ starts on Thursday, 10/12. The highest bidder will select their piece first.

You can learn more here: https://www.brightmoments.io/apophenies
